Package: movie
Title: Provides Tools for Exploring and Analyzing Summer-Themed Movies Using IMDb Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Neharika", "Shah", , "nsha0102@student.monash.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The movie package provides tools to explore and analyze summer-themed movies using IMDb data. It includes functions for filtering by genre, summarizing genre statistics,and a Shiny app for interactive exploration of trends by genre, year, and rating.
